description.p:
Lanes 3 to 6 respectively show changes over time (30, 60, 90, and 120 minutes) in the nucleotide chain achieved using the magnesium-containing sulfonic acid buffer solution;

lanes 7 to 10 respectively show changes over time (30, 60, 90, and 120 minutes) in the nucleotide chain achieved using the manganese-containing sulfonic acid buffer solution; and

Lanes 11 to 14 respectively show changes over time (30, 60, 90, and 120 minutes) in the nucleotide chain achieved using the cobalt-containing cacodylate buffer solution.
